अध्रि-गु<BR> --This is the name of a man twice referred to in the Rigveda 1) i. 112, 20; viii. 12, 2. Cf. Hopkins, Journal of the American Oriental Society, 17, 90. as a prote4ge4 of the As4vins and of Indra respectively.

