जल जातूकर्ण्य<BR> (‘descendant of Ja1tu1karn2a’), is mentioned in the S4a1n3kha1yana S4rauta Su1tra (xvi. 29, 6) as having obtained the position of Purohita, or domestic priest, of the three peoples or kings of Ka1s4i, Videha, and Kosala.

